      Constructor Class for Ticket
      Parameters:
      clientName - user name
      clientContact - user contact details
      movieTitle - title of the movie being screened
      seatID - where the seat is at
      transactionID - a unique ID corresponding to the transaction when booking ticket
      typeOfMovie - 3D and Digital
      classOfCinema - Regular/ Atmos/ Platinum
      date - a Date object containing time
      ageGroup - Student/ Adult/ Senior
      seatType - Normal/ Couple/ Elite/ Ultim
      isBlockBuster - boolean to check if a movie is a block buster
      isPreview - boolean to check if a movie is preview screening
